merlin 1.1
==========

	emacs: Ported the completion to the usual `completion-at-point'
	system, disabled auto-complete-mode-by-default

	emacs: reset now tells merlin about the current buffer name

	emacs: merlin-mode comes with a menu

	emacs: improved documentation of the mode

  backend: code cleanup

  backend: method completion

  vim plugin: refactored synchronization code out

